{
  "global": "Systematically resolve seven evolutionary-developmental biology sub-questions spanning lateral plate mesoderm fate, Hox-gene temporal and spatial expression, retinoic acid gradient signaling, and the comparative axis biology of median versus paired fins.",
  "subtasks": [
    {
      "subtask": "Predict the outcome of somatopleure rotation at HH11 (Q1)",
