        "Conclude that grafted somatopleure will respond to host Hox and signaling environment, producing limbs at positions dictated by the new A-P context rather than the original donor position"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Determine the earliest traceable cell-lineage stages for forelimb, hindlimb, and interlimb regions and identify the specific Hox genes involved (Q2)",
      "atomics": [
        "Identify that forelimb-fated lateral plate mesoderm can be traced to HH10–13, marked by expression of HOXB5 and HOXC5 in the cervico-thoracic lateral plate",
